7. Performance Metrics
Monitor EBS-specific performance issues:

-- Check for "row cache mutex" waits (common post-19c upgrade)
SELECT EVENT, TOTAL_WAITS, TIME_WAITED_MICRO FROM V$SYSTEM_EVENT WHERE EVENT LIKE '%row cache mutex%';

EVENT                                                            TOTAL_WAITS TIME_WAITED_MICRO
---------------------------------------------------------------- ----------- -----------------
row cache mutex                                                            3             24308


EVENT                                                            TOTAL_WAITS TIME_WAITED_MICRO
---------------------------------------------------------------- ----------- -----------------
row cache mutex                                                            1                 4



8. Critical MOS Documents for Scripts
Doc ID 2704990.1: E-Business Suite 19c Database Upgrade Analyzer (run pre/post-upgrade checks).
Doc ID 2552181.1: Interoperability notes for EBS 12.2 and 19c.
Doc ID 2183357.1: Reference for applying RUPs in EBS environments.

Use adgrants.sql (from EBS) to validate roles/privileges in CDB/PDB setups.
For advanced troubleshooting, use ADZDDBCC.sql (from Oracle Support) to validate EBS database consistency.